Hello Everyone, I am very new to HubSpot and HubL. I have a few questions on dealing with a JSON object in HubL.
1. How do I set a dynamic key while updating a JSON object using the update function? For example, {% do dict_var.update({dynamicKeyFromVariable: valueFromVariable}) %}
2. Is there a way to correctly pass a JSON object (table rows received from hubdb_table_rows) from HubL to javascript? Every time I use {{ tableData }} it prints an invalid JSON data. For example, {"test": "value"} gets printed as {test='some value'}.
